            "id": "4530704",
            "title": "Blackstone buys portfolio of Texas retail properties for $440M - report",
            "description": "<html><body><p data-eci=\"true\">Blackstone (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BX\" title=\"Blackstone Inc.\">BX</a></span></span>) is buying a portfolio of Texas-based retail properties for $440M, according to a media report on Thursday.</p>\n<p>The portfolio, spanning some 2M square feet, includes properties in Dallas, Houston and San Antonio, Bloomberg reported, citing one person familiar.</p>\n<p data-component=\"paragraph\">“Grocery-anchored retail is one of our high-conviction themes given the strong fundamentals across the sector,” said Adam Leslie, managing director at Blackstone Real Estate, in a statement, Bloomberg reported. “We are thrilled to acquire these high-quality assets across the largest cities in Texas.”</p>\n<p data-component=\"paragraph\">The Bloomberg <a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-12-11/blackstone-extends-bet-on-grocery-stores-in-texas-property-deal\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"report\">report</a> noted that a Blackstone (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BX\" title=\"Blackstone Inc.\">BX</a>) representative declined to comment on whom the seller of the Texas properties was, as well the deal price or other specifics regarding the transaction.</p>\n<p data-component=\"paragraph\">The alternative asset manager in February <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/20000318-blackstone-real-estate-completes-privatization-of-retail-opportunity-investments-corp-for-4\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"completed\">completed</a> a $4B take-private deal with Retail Opportunity Investments, which specializes in grocery-anchored shopping centers.</p>\n<div><div data-ad-size=\"5x24\" data-ad-status=\"rendered\" data-component=\"in-body-ad\"><div data-ad-status=\"rendered\" data-testid=\"sparkle-ad\" id=\"in-body-98866-1\" role=\"presentation\" tabindex=\"-1\"><div data-google-query-id=\"CLe5po3AtpEDFTsXigMdGo4VpA\" id=\"a44ce813f19a72b40a7c29c9299725e9\"></div></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"signup_widget_placeholder\"></div>\n</body></html>",
